{"tid":543341,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"甄子丹：我早就把美國籍退回去了，現在是百分之百的中國人！","createTime":"2018-01-28T11:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T05:12:24.000Z","uid":1886,"like":17,"dislike":108,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"f6767eb30e10f18ec7922d59b4a488a33ea66847","tid":543341,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T11:33:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">有片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://fb.com/groups/248449212217592/permalink/479072825821895/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fgroups%2F248449212217592%2Fpermalink%2F479072825821895%2F&d=5DDn6lKicMIujhLNYaocQ%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=b369faed\" target=\"_blank\">https://fb.com/groups/248449212217592/permalink/479072825821895/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20171230/large/e8907a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20171230%2Flarge%2Fe8907a.jpg&h=ae39f532&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div><br />\n<br />\n甄子丹為新戲北上宣傳，這天上中國一個電視節目，當主持人介紹他時，用「美國來的甄子丹先生」慘被他打斷，<span style=\"color: red;\">甄子丹霸氣宣佈，他不是美國人甄子丹，他是中國人甄子丹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！</span>據悉他在四年前已經放棄美國國籍，轉而加入中國國籍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20171230/20259185\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171230%2F20259185&d=5DDn6lKicMIujhLNYaocQ%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=57628f4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171230%2F20259185&h=43f8b869\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20171230/20259185</a>"},{"pid":"534201dcb50bd5a7d0a4289c9068170fa8de3650","tid":543341,"uid":53628,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T11:40:13.000Z","msg":"佢本身好似都係大陸仔黎"},{"pid":"c9a6574567b0c8e032aa38257d38219a6272b938","tid":543341,"uid":25086,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T11:41:06.000Z","msg":"賺完人仔投資移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6787c66d992a369e55e9b72b2bc6124a9b3f5947","tid":543341,"uid":4942,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T11:41:21.000Z","msg":"好做唔做做強國人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8936f8720605ba56f9c02d617b64c884f5fa48","tid":543341,"uid":65587,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T11:41:36.000Z","msg":"連泰臣都贏埋 依家返去打馬雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36351c730b6787c6221655a4b1dec3d4e502745","tid":543341,"uid":104213,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T11:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/28/194216_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F28%2F194216_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=cdd56b5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5311771397ab7ef71232f12babb355894e14249d","tid":543341,"uid":73972,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T11:43:11.000Z","msg":"其實國籍呢d野有冇得話退就退？<br />\n<br />\n佢個老婆成個港女咁，一定持雙重國籍，佢d仔女都係，一有唔對路叫老婆carry佢咪得，放棄國籍得啖笑"},{"pid":"b4337a47694653e59b156d9b4523fa00c8e64b9c","tid":543341,"uid":128035,"lik